        <p id="u400640-2">Our completely redesigned and expanded Wellness Center offers:</p>
        <ul class="list0 nls-None" id="u400640-9">
         <li id="u400640-4">State-of-the-art equipment for cardio, strength training, Pilates and more (Open 24 hours)</li>
         <li id="u400640-6">Indoor pool (6:00 a.m. to 10:00 p.m.)</li>
         <li id="u400640-8">Jacuzzi (6:00 a.m. to 10:00 p.m.)</li>
        </ul>
